Class FileLoader

java.lang.Object
utils.FileLoader
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileLoader
public class FileLoader extends Object implements IFileLoader
The FileLoader class provides methods to load data from CSV files into various models. It supports loading applicants, officers, managers, projects, enquiries, and applications.
